            <scopecontent id="aspace_e85d39b1f4f595c566d9630e7995ef4e">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The series is arranged by type. It consists of photographs, slides, and photograph albums recording the personal and professional life of Josephine Steiner Barger. The photographs section is arranged in alphabetical order by topic. The photograph albums and slides sections contain pictures of friends, vacations, her professional environment, and local life from the South Pacific in World War II and Venezuela from 1942 to 1949.</p>
            </scopecontent>
